room_title: Escape room "Vive La Résistance!" by Quandary Escape Adventures in Denton
room_description: The year is 1942. The place is Paris, France. German soldiers occupy the city. You and your comrades must help the French resistance to infiltrate a Nazi general's office and retrieve compromising documents regarding the resistance. Lives are at stake! Can you escape with the secret files before it’s too late?
